title: Picnic Time's Aviano Market Basket 648
transcripts: The Aviano Basket by Picnic Time combines a fine romance of a basket with the practicality of a collapsible insulated tote. Picnic Time's Aviano polyester microfiber on a lightweight aluminum frame. It's stylish and practical enough to take with you to the farmers market or a fine day at the  park. With this 29 can capacity, you can carry carry food and sundries to and from home. Take it to the beach for a romantic picnic or even use it as a day bag. It has a water resistant insulated interior and fully removable zipper top which makes for easy accessibility. Market basket is also fully collapsible fro easy storage or transportation when empty. It also has an exterior zipper pocket lined with the attractive Aviano pocket for extra storage. Leave your paper and plastic bags at home and hit the town with the stylish Aviano market basket.
